---Dead-End/Drag Strip/Astroblast---

Astroblast's CR repair cycle finishes. A light mist and a hiss ensue 
as the door opens up. He stretches and smiles cruelly. "Megatron, 
this is Astroblast, my repair cycle has completed and I am ready 
to serve, what is your command?" He waits.

Dead-End and Drag Strip ignore what is happening behind them. 
Drag Strip leaps into flight after Wildrider, "Hey Wildrider, show him 
the true meaning of a Stunticon light show!" he yells as he fires his 
plasma cannons at Incarcinator several times, and watches the 
purple globes in anticipation of Wildrider's scatterblaster further 
increasing the apparent spectacle.

Dead-End shakes his head at Drag Strip, "Foo--" he begins as a 
shell from Incarcinator lands right beside him throwing him 
backwards into Skyscream.
